<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    {% block stylesheets %}
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="{{ absolute_url(asset('build/app.css')) }}" />
    {% endblock %}
</head>
<body>
<section class="pt-0 pb-3">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center pt-3">
            <div class="col-lg-8">
                <div class="text-center mb-4">
                    <h1 class="mb-2">Hey 👋</h1>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col">
                <div class="row justify-content-center pt-2">
                    <div class="col-lg-8 text-center">
                        <p>Tu as oublié ton mot de passe ? Pas de panique !</p>
                        <p>Il te suffit de le changer en <strong>cliquant sur le lien suivant</strong> 👇</p>

                        <a class="btn btn-primary mb-5 mt-4" href="{{ url('app_reset_password', {token: resetToken.token}) }}">{{ url('app_reset_password', {token: resetToken.token}) }}</a>

                        <p><strong>Attention</strong>, ce lien expirera automatiquement dans {{ resetToken.expirationMessageKey|trans(resetToken.expirationMessageData, 'ResetPasswordBundle') }}.<br><br></p>

                        <p>
                            À bientôt !<br>
                            Fanny ❤️<br><br>
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
</section>
<section class="pb-4 bg-primary-alt has-divider" id="footer">
    <div class="divider flip-y">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" width="100%" height="96px" viewBox="0 0 100 100" version="1.1" preserveAspectRatio="none" class="injected-svg bg-white" data-src="assets/img/dividers/divider-2.svg">
            <path d="M0,0 C16.6666667,66 33.3333333,99 50,99 C66.6666667,99 83.3333333,66 100,0 L100,100 L0,100 L0,0 Z"></path>
        </svg>
    </div>
    <div class="container pt-0 pb-0">
        <div class="row mb-4 justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-auto">
                <a href="{{ absolute_url(path('app_home')) }}" target="_blank">
                    <img class="logo-img" src="{{ absolute_url(asset('build/images/logos/logo.png')) }}" alt="Le Réhausseur" />
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row mb-4">
            <div class="col">
                <ul class="nav justify-content-center">
                    <li class="nav-item"><a href="#" class="nav-link">Me désabonner</a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
</body>
</html>





